<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.10.5">
<l>pāriṉai yuṇṭu pāriṉai yumiḻntu pārataṅ kaiyeṟin torukāl</l>
<l>tēriṉai yūrntu tēriṉait turanta ceṅkaṇmāl ceṉṟuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>ērnirai vayaḷuḷ vāḷaikaḷ maṟuki yemakkiṭa maṉṟiteṉ ṟeṇṇi</l>
<l>cīrmali poykai ceṉṟaṇai kiṉṟa tiruveḷḷi yaṅkuṭi yatuvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where dwells bright-eyed Māl who, having eaten the earth</l>
<l rend="indent">and expelled the earth,</l>
<l>Put chariots to flight, having destroyed an army in the Bhārata [War],</l>
<l rend="indent">arriving one time driving a chariot,</l>
<l>Is that very one - Tiruveḷḷiyaṅkuṭi where, in paddy fields with ploughed rows,</l>
<l rend="indent">the vāḷai [fish], turning [around],</l>
<l>Thinking, “This is not a place for us,” are crowding [together],</l>
<l rend="indent">having moved into fine, full pools.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
